  "description": "TailWatch — InSAR ground-deformation monitoring & early-warning for tailings dams and pit walls (SBAS displacement, velocity maps, inverse-velocity failure forecasting, GISTM-aligned TARP alarms). Didactic + decision-support, not a certified safety system.",
